        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ban Corporate PACs Act &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill prohibits for-profit corporations from establishing or operating a separate segregated political fund (commonly known as a political action committee or PAC). Existing funds must terminate not later than one year after the date of enactment of this bill.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
